day1.dayDesc: Breezy this morning; cloudy with a couple of showers, mainly early in the day
day1.nightDesc: Mostly cloudy with occasional rain and drizzle late

day3.dayDesc: Cloudy and breezy with a couple of showers, mainly early in the day

day5.dayDesc: Still cloudy with a shower in spots in the morning, then becoming breezy
